summary: it hasn’t even been a month
title: it hasn’t even been a month
body:
I can’t believe it! A month ago, all Micheal Sheen was to me was that gay vampire villain from Twilight and now, now he is the gay angel boyfriend who would treat me RIGHT! 

The Good Omens tv show, like the book, is amazing amazing amazing but this is a Michael Sheen appreciation post. Like - what the hell. He is really THAT bitch. Just like everything he does is perfect and I can’t deal with it - this is how actors are supposed to interact with us crazies! Much love to him. 

also he is definitely crushing on David Tennant which is just relatable af
